name: Wishlink Pixel
author: Wishlink

sections.description: Wishlink(WL) Pixel tracks the purchases from the traffic sent by WL affiliated sources, made on the woocommerce enabled website. All the affiliate transaction information are also sent to Wishlink.
sections.installation:
Upload the Wishlink plugin to your website, activate it, and then enter your unique website name and currency in which you sell your products.
You’re done!
sections.faq:
Q. Do the wishlink Pixel tracks user info?
A. No! We do not track any user info, we only capture the order related information and the interaction of user with site.

short_description: Wishlink Pixel is your one stop solution to calculate ROI on affiliate marketing spend!
